articles.title: Michelle Williams Narrating Audiobook of Britney Spears’ Memoir: ‘I Stand With Britney’ - Variety
articles.description: Michelle Williams will narrate Britney Spears' upcoming memoir, 'The Woman in Me.' Spears will record an introduction.
articles.content:
Following her Oscar-nominated turn in Steven Spielberg’s “The Fabelmans,” Michelle Williams will next embody the voice of Britney Spears by narrating her upcoming memoir, “The Woman in Me.”
